 Ireland]] in 1979 and his remains were found in October 2010 in the townland of Carrickrobin, near Hackballscross, [[County Louth]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Remains were 'Disappeared' Crossmaglen man Gerry Evans|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-northern-ireland-11866971|agency=[[BBC News]]|date=29 November 2010|accessdate=20 December 2010}}</ref>\n|No / Murdered\n|data-sort-value=\"11315\"|31 years\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"1979\"|1979\n|[[Murder of Michelle Busha|Michelle Busha]]\n|18\n|Michelle Busha left home in December 1979 after an argument with her father in Bacy City, Texas. She was murdered in May 1980 while hitchhiking in Blue Earth, Minnesota and remained unidentified until 2015.<ref name=who>Erickson, David. \u201cRunaway Jane.\u201d ''Who Killed Jane Doe?'', season 1, episode 6, [[Investigation Discovery]], 4 Apr. 2017.</ref> \n|No / Murdered\n|data-sort-value=\"12775\"|35 years\n|}\n\n==1980s==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable zebra\"\n|-\n! data-sort-type=\"isoDate\"|Date\n! data-sort-type=\"text\"|Person(s)\n! data-sort-type=\"text\"|Age \n! class=\"unsortable\"|Circumstances\n! data-sort-type=\"text\"|Found alive / cause of death\n! data-sort-type=\"value\"|Time spent missing or unconfirmed\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"1980-02-13\"|1980\n|[[Murder of Marcia King|Marcia King]]\n|18\n|Marcia King left home in Little Rock, Arkansas at an unknown date in 1980. She traveled across the United States and was murdered in Troy, Ohio in April 1981 at the age of 21. King's body remained unidentified until 2018.<ref name=\"tdn\">{{cite news|last1=Vallieu|first1=Melody|title='Buckskin Girl' identified|url=http://www.tdn-net.com/top-stories/39213/buckskin-girl-identified|accessdate=12 April 2018|work=Troy Daily News|date=11 April 2018}}</ref>\n|No / Murdered\n| data-sort-value=\"13505\"|37 years\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"1980-02-13\"|1980\n|[[Timothy White (abduction victim)|Timothy White]]\n|data-sort-value=\"005\"|5\n|Timothy White disappeared on 13 February 1980 and it 