the couple's home in [[Wheaton, Illinois]]. In 1987, workers drained a pond 4 blocks from the Pappas' house and found the car with Carole's body inside. It is theorized that she mistook a driveway near the pond for one leading to her neighborhhood, and that she may have been drinking.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1987-08-08/news/8702280308_1_mrs-pappas-carole-pappas-retention-pond|title=Pappas car found|accessdate=6 May 2018}}</ref>\n|No / Drowned\n| data-sort-value=\"1825\"|5 years\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"1983-07-19\"|1983\n|William Howard Hughes\n|33\n|William Hughes, a [[United States Air Force officer rank insignia|United States Air Force officer]] with security clearance and expertise in rocket self-destruct technology, vanished after departing on a trip to [[Europe]]. Authorities feared he had [[Defection|defected]] to the [[Soviet Union]] or had been abducted by its agents. In June 2018, he was found living in [[California]] under an assumed name.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://amp.usatoday.com/amp/689776002|accessdate=11 June 2018|title=U.S. Air Force fugitive missing for 35 years found living in California|date=11 June 2018|publisher=USAToday}}</ref>\n|Yes\n| data-sort-value=\"12775\"|35 years\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"1984-06-01\"|1984\n|[[Murder of Mark Tildesley|Mark Tildesley]]\n|data-sort-value=\"007\"|7\n|Mark Tildesley disappeared while visiting a funfair in [[Berkshire|Wokingham, Berkshire, England]] on the evening of 1 June 1984. He was lured away from the fair and his bicycle was found chained to railings nearby.<ref name=BBC570385>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/570385.stm|title=Cooke: The predatory paedophile|work=[[BBC News]]|date=17 December 1999|accessdate=22 April 2015}}</ref> In 1990 it emerged that Mark had been [[Child abduction|abducted]], drugged, [[torture]]d, [[rape]]d and [[murder]]ed by a [[London]]-based [[Pedophilia|paedophile]] [[gang]] on the night he disappeared.<ref name=BBC570385/><ref>{{cite w