ound\">{{cite news|last=Portman|first=Jennifer|title=FLDE special agent: 'Mike Williams was murdered'|url=http://www.tallahassee.com/story/news/2017/12/20/fdle-give-update-mike-williams-disappearance/968920001|newspaper=[[Tallahassee Democrat]]|date=20 December 2017|accessdate=20 December 2017}}</ref> On 8 May 2018, police arrested Williams' former wife, who had remarried. After a four-day trial in December 2018, she was convicted of murder, conspiracy, and accessory after the fact.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Etters|first1=Karl|last2=Portman|first2=Jennifer|title='Justice for Michael': 18 years later, Florida woman found guilty in plot to kill husband|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2018/12/14/denise-williams-trial-verdict-guilty-mike-williams-murder-case-jury/2319970002/|newspaper=[[USA Today]]|date=December 14, 2018|accessdate=December 15, 2018}}</ref>\n|No / Murdered\n|17 Years\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"2001-04-27|2001\n|[[Murder of Erica Green|Erica Green]]\n|data-sort-value=\"003\"|3\n|[[Murder]] victim whose [[Decapitation|decapitated]] body was discovered on 28 April 2001, in [[Kansas City, Missouri]], 12 to 48 hours after death. Her head was found in a trash bag nearby on 1 May 2001.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2005/US/05/05/precious.doe/index.html|title=CNN.com \u2013 Mother, stepfather charged in 'Precious Doe' killing \u2013 May 5, 2005|website=www.cnn.com|access-date=2017-12-21}}</ref> The victim remained unidentified until 5 May 2005.\n|No / Murdered\n|1 - 2 days\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"2001-05-01|2001\n|[[Chandra Levy]]\n|data-sort-value=\"024\"|24\n|An American [[Internship|intern]] at the [[Federal Bureau of Prisons]] in Washington, D.C. who disappeared in May 2001. Her skeletal remains were found in [[Rock Creek Park]] on 22 May 2002.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://articles.latimes.com/2002/may/23/nation/na-chandra23|title=Remains in D.C. Park Identified as Intern's|last=BRAUN|first=STEPHEN|date=23 May 2002|work=Los Angeles Times|acce