6\" |56\n|Discovered naked and beaten and with severe amnesia on 31 August 2004, at a [[Burger King]] in [[Richmond Hill, Georgia]];<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/local/os-benjamin-kyle-amnesia-identified-20150921-story.html|title=No-man's land: Amnesia stole his identity for 11 years|last=Hudak|first=Stephen|work=OrlandoSentinel.com|access-date=2017-09-14|language=en-US}}</ref> after efforts from genetic genealogists, his true identity was finally discovered on 16 September 2015.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.news4jax.com/news/benjamin-kyle-writes-thank-you-post|title=Benjamin Kyle writes 'Thank You' post|last=Mohrmann|first=Kent Justice, Jodi|date=16 September 2015|work=WJXT|access-date=2017-09-14|language=en-US}}</ref> Powell had forgotten his identity and had been living under the name \"Benjaman Kyle\".\n|Yes\n|Unclear\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"2005-01-01\" |2005\n|[[Margie Profet]]\n| data-sort-value=\"046\" |46\n|An [[evolutionary biologist]] who had ceased contact with her family in 2002 and had last been seen in [[Cambridge, Massachusetts]] in 2005. In May 2012 she was told by a friend about her \"disappearance\" and contacted her family. She had been living in an isolated location, suffering from a physical ailment that caused her severe pain, and had not realized she was considered \"missing\".<ref name=\"psychologytoday.com\">Mike Martin, [http://www.psychologytoday.com/articles/201204/the-mysterious-case-the-vanishing-genius The Mysterious Case of the Vanishing Genius]. ''Psychology Today'', May 2012.</ref><ref name=\"blogs.nature.com\">Brendan Maher, [http://blogs.nature.com/news/2012/05/missing-biologist-surfaces-reunites-with-family.html Missing Biologist Surfaces, Reunites with Family.] ''Nature'', 31 May 2012.</ref>\n|Yes\n|7 Years out of contact\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"2005-02-24\" |2005\n|[[Murder of Jessica Lunsford|Jessica Lunsford]]\n| data-sort-value=\"009\" |9\n|An American girl who was abducted from her home in [