910.html|title=The body of missing Russian tycoon Leonid Rozhetskin has been found.|date=18 November 2013|work=The Independent|access-date=2017-08-16|language=en-GB}}</ref>\n|No\n|5 Years\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"2008-07-15\" |2008\n|[[Death of Caylee Anthony|Caylee Anthony]]\n| data-sort-value=\"002\" |2\n|Caylee was reported missing on 15 July 2008 in [[Orlando|Orlando, Florida]]. On 11 December 2008, her skeletal remains were found with a blanket inside a trash bag in a wooded area near the family home.<ref name=\"remains\">{{cite news|title=Duct Tape Found Stuck To Mouth of Child's Remains |publisher=wftv.com |date= 12\u201313 December 2008 |accessdate=27 August 2011|url=http://www.wftv.com/news/18264817/detail.html |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110903232101/http://www.wftv.com/news/18264817/detail.html |archivedate=3 September 2011 }}</ref><ref name=\"Closing\">{{cite web|url=http://articles.cnn.com/2011-07-03/justice/florida.casey.anthony.trial_1_casey-anthony-caylee-jurors?_s=PM:CRIME |title=Prosecution, defense offer closing arguments in Casey Anthony trial |accessdate=17 September 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010002626/http://articles.cnn.com/2011-07-03/justice/florida.casey.anthony.trial_1_casey-anthony-caylee-jurors?_s=PM%3ACRIME |archivedate=10 October 2012 }}</ref> H[[Death of Caylee Anthony|er mother was accused but acquitted of her murder.]]\n|No\n|5 Months\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"2009-02-01\" |2009\n|[[Gerry Rafferty]]\n| data-sort-value=\"061\" |61\n|Scottish singer-songwriter, who was reported as having been missing for seven months in February 2009, having disappeared from [[St Thomas' Hospital]] in London, where he was being treated for liver failure.<ref>{{cite web|title=Fears growing for missing Baker Street singer Gerry Rafferty|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/4635285/Fears-growing-for-missing-Baker-Street-singer-Gerry-Rafferty.html|website=The Telegraph|accessdate