 After Conrado Juarez Confesses To Daughter's Murder|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/10/15/margarita-castillo-baby-hope-murder_n_4100207.html|accessdate=10 September 2014|agency=Huffington Post|date=15 October 2013}}</ref>\n|No / Murdered\n|-\n|1991\n|[[Murder of Margaret Perry|Margaret Perry]]\n|26\n|Margaret Perry was from [[Portadown]], [[County Armagh]], Northern Ireland; she disappeared on 21 June 1991. After a tip from the [[Provisional Irish Republican Army|IRA]], her body was found buried across the [[Republic of Ireland\u2013United Kingdom border|border]] in a field in [[Mullaghmore, County Sligo]], Ireland, on 30 June 1992. She had been beaten to death. Her murder has never been solved.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/magazine/1994/05/08/the-troublesome-death-of-margaret-perry/4473da4a-df3f-4d19-995c-79c8f51fbe43/|title=THE TROUBLESOME DEATH OF MARGARET PERRY|last=Coll|first=Steve|date=1994-05-08|work=Washington Post|access-date=2019-10-06|language=en-US|issn=0190-8286}}</ref>\n|No / Murdered\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"1991-06-29\"|1991\n|[[Murder of Sheree Beasley|Sheree Beasley]]\n|6\n|Sheree Beasley, an Australian schoolgirl from [[Rosebud, Victoria|Rosebud]] was kidnapped, raped, and murdered by a man named Robert Lowe on 29 June 1991,<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/leader/south-east/mornington-peninsula-unites-to-mark-rosebud-murder-victim-sheree-beasleys-30th-birthday/news-story/0da24abeaa315042edacd9364ad67291|title=Murdered girl Sheree Beasley remembered|access-date=2017-07-16}}</ref> and her body was found weeks later on 24 September in a [[stormwater drain]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.psychology.org.au/Assets/Files/crime_related_confidentiality_ethics.pdf|title=Wayback Machine|date=28 January 2015|access-date=2017-07-16|url-status=bot: unknown|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128115203/http://www.psychology.org.au/Assets/Files/crime_related_confidentiality_ethics.pdf|archiv