der the Belgian law, is most of the time not fully served in prison but later on changed into a [[suspended sentence]]).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.blikopdewereld.nl/rechtspraak/70-levenslange-gevangenisstraf/536-hoe-lang-duurt-levenslange-gevangenisstraf-in-belgie.html|title=Invuloefening Feniks Hoofdstuk 1 Van vuistbijl tot sikkel \u2013 Blik op de Wereld|website=www.blikopdewereld.nl}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.lesoir.be/actualite/belgique/assises-de-liege-l-assassin-2008-06-10-604850.shtml|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080613024343/http://www.lesoir.be/actualite/belgique/assises-de-liege-l-assassin-2008-06-10-604850.shtml|url-status=dead|title=\"Ait Oud, reconnu coupable, s'effondre\" (lesoir.be)|archivedate=13 June 2008}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.lesoir.be/actualite/belgique/deliberation-sur-la-peine-au-2008-06-11-604935.shtml|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080613235013/http://www.lesoir.be/actualite/belgique/deliberation-sur-la-peine-au-2008-06-11-604935.shtml|url-status=dead|title=\"La perp\u00e9tuit\u00e9 pour Abdallah Ait Oud\" (lesoir.be)|archivedate=13 June 2008}}</ref>\n|No / Murdered\n|18 Days \n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"2006-06-18\" |2006\n|[[Death of Chanel Petro-Nixon|Chanel Petro-Nixon]]\n| data-sort-value=\"016\" |16 or 17\n|An American teenager from [[Brooklyn|Brooklyn, New York]], who went missing on 18 June 2006. Her body was discovered on 22 June 2006 in a [[Bin bag|trash bag]] in front of 212 Kingston Avenue. It was determined that Petro-Nixon had been [[strangled]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/2006/06/24/2006-06-24_body_found_in_bag_idd_as_studious_bklyn_.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080401094128/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/2006/06/24/2006-06-24_body_found_in_bag_idd_as_studious_bklyn_.html|url-status=dead|archive-date=2008-04-01|title=BODY FOUND IN BAG ID'D AS STUDIOUS B'KLYN GIRL \u2013 News \u2013 NY Daily News|date=1 April 2008|access-date=2017-09-08}